@rhatdan, let's find consensus if we want to add that and how it would look like.

While I think the feature per se is out of scope for Podman, it does sound attractive for the REST use case.  Hence, I'd suggest to make this a REST-only feature and not expose it on the CLI; Skopeo should be used there.

@jwhonce @baude @mheon WDYT?
